      </p></div><div><p><a title="Companies > miHoYo [211 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/mihoyo">miHoYo</a> has released a new trailer for cosmic life <a title="Genres > Simulation [865 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/genres/simulation">simulation game</a> <em><a title="Games > Petit Planet [2 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/petit-planet">Petit Planet</a></em> showcasing the game’s planet building. <span id="more-1005292"></span></p><p>“Plant a planet to call your own, and nurture it into the planet of your dreams,” reads the trailer description. “Shining among the countless stars is a life we’ve always longed for.”</p><p>The “<a href="https://www.gematsu.com/2025/10/petit-planet-coziness-test-begins-november-7">Coziness Test</a>” closed beta test for <em>Petit Planet</em> also just went live for <a title="Platforms > PC [24,735 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a> and iOS. Sign-ups and pre-registration are still available via the <a href="https://planet.hoyoverse.com/" target="_blank">official website</a>.</p><p>Watch the trailer below.</p><h2><span>Planet Design Trailer</span></h2><p><strong>English</strong></p><!-- AD: content -->
